# Copy to `.env.local` (local dev) or `.env.production` (production build on the server).
# Vite loads these automatically when you run `pnpm run build` in this package.

# --- API base (session notes / AI) ---
# Leave UNSET when the SPA is served from the same origin as the API and nginx (or similar)
# proxies `/api` to the Node server (recommended for abanoteassistant.com-style deploys).
#
# Set to the API ORIGIN ONLY (no path, no trailing slash) when the browser cannot use same-origin `/api`:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-api-host.example.com
#
# After changing this, rebuild the SPA. It is baked in at build time.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
